### Health check
GET http://localhost:3333/api/v1/health

### Login as elector
POST http://localhost:3333/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "elector@example.com",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### Get current user
GET http://localhost:3333/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer demo-elector-token

### List elections
GET http://localhost:3333/api/v1/elections
Authorization: Bearer demo-elector-token

### Get ballot
GET http://localhost:3333/api/v1/elections/2a3c4d5e-1111-4a4a-bbbb-111111111111/ballot
Authorization: Bearer demo-elector-token

### Submit vote
POST http://localhost:3333/api/v1/votes
Authorization: Bearer demo-elector-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "electionId": "2a3c4d5e-1111-4a4a-bbbb-111111111111",
  "selections": [
    {
      "positionId": "8f7a6b5c-1111-4c4c-aaaa-222222222222",
      "candidateId": "10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000010"
    }
  ],
  "encryptedBallot": "base64:ZXhhbXBsZS1lbmNyeXB0ZWQtYmFsbG90",
  "ballotCommitment": "0xnew-ballot-commitment-001",
  "nullifier": "0xnew-nullifier-001",
  "clientTimestamp": "2026-04-03T13:30:00.000Z",
  "deviceInfo": {
    "platform": "web",
    "appVersion": "0.1.0"
  }
}

### Verify receipt (public endpoint)
GET http://localhost:3333/api/v1/verification/receipts/9d9b9f9a-1111-4222-8333-444444444444

### Audit ledger (public endpoint)
GET http://localhost:3333/api/v1/audit/elections/2a3c4d5e-1111-4a4a-bbbb-111111111111/ledger
